x+2x^2+3x^3+\cdots = x \frac{d}{dx} (x+x^2+x^3+x^4+\cdots)
x+x^2+x^3+x^4 + \cdots = \frac{x}{1-x} 
x+2x^2+3x^3+\cdots = x \frac{d}{dx} \left(\frac{x}{1-x}\right)
x+2x^2+3x^3+\cdots = \frac{x}{(1-x)^2}
